  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A tapping script for Day 16 of the money arc. The script works with the belief that abundance is available to everyone except you — the envy and frustration of watching money reach other people while it seems to skip past."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "New to tapping? Read "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"}}],
            "text": "how EFT tapping works"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " first."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Karate chop"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I believe money happens for others but not for me, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I feel left out of abundance, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Even though I fear I'll always be the exception, I deeply and completely accept myself."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tapping round"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I watch other people making money."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I wonder why it skips me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I think I'm missing something the rest of them have."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I feel stuck on the outside looking in."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I've told myself it's just not for me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I feel envy and frustration."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I'm ready to release that belief."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I don't want to live as the exception."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Eyebrow:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " Wealth is available to everyone — including me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Side of eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I open to the same flow that reaches others."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under eye:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I trust that abundance includes me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under nose:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I welcome my share."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Chin:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I am as worthy as anyone who has it."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Collarbone:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I claim space in the flow of wealth."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Under arm:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I expect money to find me."}]}]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Top of head:"}, {"type": "text", "text": " I belong in the circle of abundance."}]}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Tap the round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times."}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 16 of "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [{"type": "italic"}],
            "text": "MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program to Attract Cash, Overflow & Abundance Without Hustle or Burnout"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " (Rebecca J Page, 2025). The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), developed in the mid-1990s."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
